==English==

{{wikipediapar|Alternativism}}

===Noun===
'''alternativism'''
# An ideology of limitless [[alternatives]].
# The belief in practicing a specific alternative.
# Rejecting the [[social normality]].

====Usage notes====
While this may seem like a [[protologism]] the word '''alternativism''' has been implied, if not used, for decades now. The term itself is merely a [[canopy word]] meant to cover the variety of applications for different [[w:Alternative|Alternatives]]. It's most common usage or [[acknowledgement]] is in the context of specific alternative practices. An early [[endorsement]] of the term arose from analyzing alternative [[medicine]] movements. [http://www.csicop.org/si/9509/alternativism.html]

